Emmerdale kidnap and revenge: 10 spoilers you need to know next week


Emotions are always running high in Emmerdale – but this week could prove more tearful than usual as the locals gather to say their final farewells to their beloved friend Edna Birch. 


Elsewhere, there’s another obstacle placed in Robron’s path – and it’s a pretty big one while Rhona’s feelings are a bit muddled to say the least. Meanwhile, Rakesh finds himself on the end of Cain’s wrath while Emma’s horrific lie takes on a life of its own.



With so much going on, we have been our usual kind selves and rounded up the most important action from the village for the week commencing Monday 9th May:


